io.sphere.sdk.orders

Interface Order

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CartLike<Order>, CreationTimestamped, Custom, Identifiable<Order>, Referenceable<Order>, Resource<Order>, ResourceIdentifiable<Order>, ResourceView<Order,Order>, Timestamped, Versioned<Order>

    public interface Order
extends CartLike<Order>
    An order can be created from a cart, usually after a checkout process has been completed. Orders can also be imported.

    An order can have custom fields.

    See Also:
    Cart, OrderFromCartCreateCommand, OrderDeleteCommand, OrderImportCommand, OrderUpdateCommand, OrderByIdGet, OrderQuery
